<font color="#FF0000">RULES</font><br>
<tt>Wed Jul 23 16:03:45 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
To a  large degree the &quot;rules&quot; regarding boys and girls that Raelene grew up with are outdated . Women have more opportunities to become who they want to be than they ever have before. Nonetheless, women still have an inborn  instinct to be &quot;homemakers&quot;, regardless of how they were brought up. Men and women have always been different and always will be. It is time we realized that and stopped trying to alter nature.
